  "prompt": "Which is the best smartphone under \u20b912,000?",
  "response": "Choosing the best smartphone under \u20b912,000 depends on your specific needs, such as camera quality, battery life, performance, and display quality. As of October 2023, here are some top options available in the Indian market that offer excellent value for money within this budget:\n\n### 1. **Redmi Note 12**\n\n- **Display:** 6.67-inch Full HD+ AMOLED, 120Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor:** MediaTek Dimensity 1080\n- **RAM:** 6GB / 8GB\n- **Storage:** 128GB (expandable via microSD)\n- **Camera:** Triple Rear Cameras (50MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro)\n- **Battery:** 5000mAh with 67W fast charging\n- **Key Features:** AMOLED display with high refresh rate, strong performance for multitasking and gaming, good battery life with fast charging.\n\n### 2. **Realme 10 Pro**\n\n- **Display:** 6.72-inch Full HD+ Super AMOLED, 120Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor:** Qualcomm Snapdragon 695\n- **RAM:** 6GB / 8GB\n- **Storage:** 128GB (expandable via microSD)\n- **Camera:** Triple Rear Cameras (108MP main, 2MP depth, 2MP macro)\n- **Battery:** 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n- **Key Features:** High-resolution front and rear cameras, vibrant Super AMOLED display, balanced performance for daily tasks and moderate gaming.\n\n### 3. **Poco M4 Pro**\n\n- **Display:** 6.43-inch Full HD+ AMOLED, 90Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor:** MediaTek Helio G96\n- **RAM:** 6GB / 8GB\n- **Storage:** 64GB / 128GB (expandable via microSD)\n- **Camera:** Dual Rear Cameras (50MP main, 2MP depth)\n- **Battery:** 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n- **Key Features:** Sharp and colorful AMOLED display, good performance for gaming and multitasking, reliable battery life.\n\n### 4. **Samsung Galaxy F23**\n\n- **Display:** 6.6-inch Full HD+ TFT LCD, 120Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor:** Qualcomm Snapdragon 750G\n- **RAM:** 6GB / 8GB\n- **Storage:** 128GB (expandable via microSD)\n- **Camera:** Triple Rear Cameras (50MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro)\n- **Battery:** 5000mAh with 25W fast charging\n- **Key Features:** Trusted Samsung brand with One UI, solid camera setup, decent performance and battery life.\n\n### 5. **Motorola Moto G82**\n\n- **Display:** 6.6-inch Full HD+ OLED, 120Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor:** Qualcomm Snapdragon 695\n- **RAM:** 6GB\n- **Storage:** 128GB (expandable via microSD)\n- **Camera:** Triple Rear Cameras (50MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro)\n- **Battery:** 5000mAh with 30W fast charging\n- **Key Features:** Near-stock Android experience, vibrant OLED display, reliable performance and battery.\n\n---\n\n**Tips for Choosing the Best Smartphone:**\n\n1. **Identify Your Priorities:** Decide what's most important to you\u2014camera quality, gaming performance, battery life, or display quality.\n\n2. **Check Reviews:** Look for user reviews and expert opinions to gauge real-world performance and reliability.\n\n3. **Consider Future Updates:** Brands that regularly update their software can provide better security and new features over time.\n\n4. **Warranty and Support:** Ensure the manufacturer offers good customer support and warranty services in your region.\n\n5. **Compare Prices:** Prices can fluctuate based on sales, discounts, and availability. It's worth comparing prices across different retailers.\n\n---\n\n**Note:** Prices and availability may vary based on location and ongoing promotions. It's advisable to check the latest prices and user reviews before making a purchase.",
